article.headline: Robert Morris 72, Bryant 47
article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- Jimmy Langhurst scored 17 points to lead Robert Morris to a 72-47 victory over Bryant on Thursday night. Bateko Francisco and Mezie Nwigwe each scored 10 points for Robert Morris (14-7), which shot 68 percent (15-for-22) in the first half and led 41-22 at the break. Robert Morris led by as many as 30 points in the second half. Nick Pontes scored 10 points and nine players figured in the scoring for Bryant (4-17), which shot 35 percent in the loss.
